{"id":636876,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【cdtv】公民记者李泽华于武汉住所被捕-系前央视主/","date":"2020-02-27T09:15:39Z","modified":"2020-02-27T10:28:15Z","title":"【CDTV】2月26日公民记者李泽华于武汉住所被捕  系前央视主持人","content":"<p>2月26日晚，正在武汉进行持续报道的vlogger、公民记者<strong>李泽华</strong>的住所遭当地公安人士（自称）强行进入，本人疑似被抓捕，失去人身自由。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn4UUAAp2yI.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636877\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn4UUAAp2yI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn4UUAAp2yI.jpeg 544w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn4UUAAp2yI-240x300.jpeg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>李泽华在警方进入住所前持续在youtube进行着直播，记录了下自己的一段发言。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn5UwAAeo_B.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636879\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn5UwAAeo_B.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn5UwAAeo_B.jpeg 510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn5UwAAeo_B-225x300.jpeg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn5U0AAAVb7.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636878\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn5U0AAAVb7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn5U0AAAVb7.jpeg 510w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/ERwnUn5U0AAAVb7-225x300.jpeg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%BD%E5%8D%8E?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#李泽华</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/LiZehua?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#LiZehua</a></p>\n<p>another citizen journalist covering <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/COVID2019?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#COVID2019</a> in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/wuhan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#wuhan</a> disappeared last night  <br />He did not stop streaming until last minute.<a href=\"https://t.co/T6Iv55KHVY\">pic.twitter.com/T6Iv55KHVY</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 巴丢草  Badiucao (@badiucao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1232818914960142336?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 27, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">方斌，陈秋实，李泽华。</p>\n<p>后图是李泽华被带走前的留言。</p>\n<p>武汉前线说真话的几乎都这样了。</p>\n<p>微博关于他的帖子删除非常快。 <a href=\"https://t.co/re4DZifxCi\">pic.twitter.com/re4DZifxCi</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 武汉普通人 (@Onebtcer) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Onebtcer/status/1232903649229062144?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 27, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">我是 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%BD%E5%8D%8E?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#李泽华</a> 的朋友，希望广大网友能够持续关注李泽华事件，不要让这样一名勇于发声的新闻工作者无声消失！</p>\n<p>李泽华是继陈秋实、方斌之后，第三位被国安抓捕的武汉公民记者。他到武汉后，曾暗访青山殡仪馆的天价搬尸工招聘内幕，也曾采访处于舆论漩涡的百步亭小区。 <a href=\"https://t.co/NDr7GksT4M\">pic.twitter.com/NDr7GksT4M</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 小婷 (@ttingxiao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ttingxiao/status/1232854470066749440?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 27, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>从李泽华的往期视频看，他曾探访过武汉百步亭社区、武汉火葬场及武汉火车站地库：</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"百步亭社區和武軟的真相揭秘！ 實拍武漢Wuhan：I went to a community of Wuhan and check it out what happened.\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ItRkxFyUYVQ?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe title=\"武漢火葬場探秘：天價搬尸工招聘的真相！（Plus:街頭攙扶倒地男子記錄）COVID-19: Exploring Wuhans funeral homes.\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zyzsKSaXmtQ?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe title=\"武昌站地庫潛入：外來務工的滯留者還在不在？（Plus:流落街頭的他與它）COVID 19: What’s happened to Wuchang station&#039;s stranded workers?\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/o5RkMVTjwkc?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>几期视频后他就发出求救信息 声称遭到身份不明人员的追踪：</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"SOS 紧急求救 我正在被追\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XWrMZH9Xu6k?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>直到警方上门搜查：</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"我正在被搜查！！！我正在被搜查！！！\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/np8ZOQATLGY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>据<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%BD%E5%8D%8E/23323718?noadapt=1\">百度百科</a>显示：李泽华毕业于中国传媒大学，曾担任过央视主持人，2018年创立自媒体不服TV，开始成为视频内容创作者。李泽华是近期继陈秋实、方斌之后，另一名（公众所知的）在武汉被捕的公民记者。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"8V5I7ncS0c\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/01/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3%e4%b8%8a%e5%93%aa%e6%88%91%e7%ae%a1%e4%b8%8d%e7%9d%80-%e4%bd%86%e6%98%af%e6%88%91%e9%99%88%e7%a7%8b%e5%ae%9e%e6%9d%a5%e4%ba%86/\">【CDTV】习近平上哪我管不着 但是我陈秋实来了</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【CDTV】习近平上哪我管不着 但是我陈秋实来了》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/01/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3%e4%b8%8a%e5%93%aa%e6%88%91%e7%ae%a1%e4%b8%8d%e7%9d%80-%e4%bd%86%e6%98%af%e6%88%91%e9%99%88%e7%a7%8b%e5%ae%9e%e6%9d%a5%e4%ba%86/embed/#?secret=8V5I7ncS0c\" data-secret=\"8V5I7ncS0c\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"ZPDKen1lRy\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%89%e6%96%b9%e5%bd%ac/\">【众人推】“真公民记者” 武汉市民方斌</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【众人推】“真公民记者” 武汉市民方斌》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%b1%89%e6%96%b9%e5%bd%ac/embed/#?secret=ZPDKen1lRy\" data-secret=\"ZPDKen1lRy\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"iQlOzSryU6\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e6%96%b0%e5%8d%8e%e7%a4%be-%e3%80%8a%e5%a4%a7%e5%9b%bd%e6%88%98%e7%96%ab%e3%80%8b%e8%bf%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%87%ba%e7%89%88/\">新华社 |《大国战“疫”》近期出版</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《新华社 |《大国战“疫”》近期出版》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e6%96%b0%e5%8d%8e%e7%a4%be-%e3%80%8a%e5%a4%a7%e5%9b%bd%e6%88%98%e7%96%ab%e3%80%8b%e8%bf%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%87%ba%e7%89%88/embed/#?secret=iQlOzSryU6\" data-secret=\"iQlOzSryU6\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a class=\"st_tag internal_tag\" title=\"Posts tagged with CDS档案\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/cds%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88/\" rel=\"tag\">CDS档案</a>|<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\">武汉肺炎</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-632597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38912,38927,39707],"tags":[39595,20908,39764,39872,39871,39648,9212,38726]}